I love the shape, the design, the colour (obviously as white is my all time favourite colour, as you all know), the glittering angel wings, PLUS it has stretch! 

This is for sure going to be my absolute favourite denim jacket this summer 👌🏼

If it involves 90s denim, I’m in.

I love a light wash denim, Infact I love most denim washes with the exception of stone wash. Who remembers stone wash? Did you like it?

June has finally arrived which means summer is about to start (officially it’s the 21st June but what’s a few days between friends 😬)

I love the month of June mainly because it my birthday 😂

For me this year it’s all about lightweight fabrics, with lots of accessories (well it wouldn’t be me without them would it) and a healthy dose of denim.

I’m hoping that we have a summer similar to that of 1976 🥵☀️ 

Was this the same year that we had the infamous Ladybird Plague? 🤷🏼‍♀️

🐞Let me know if you remember.

In the meantime, here’s some Pinterest inspiration to tickle your taste buds for the hot months ahead.
